name: Matthew Davis
story: Ashton Warren grew up in a small town in rural England. He knew from a young age that he wanted to join the military and serve his country. After completing basic training, he proved to be an exceptional missile specialist, and was quickly promoted to the rank of Corporal. Ashton is known for his determination and attention to detail, making him an invaluable asset to his unit. In his free time, he enjoys hiking and exploring the countryside.
